    <h1 id="abouthead">About</h1>
    <p id="abouttext1">
        This web app is an online expense tracker created in partial 
        fulfillment of the requirements of CCAPDEV S11 Term 2 AY 2021-2022.
        Users can log in their expenses, savings, and income and track
        their balance in real time. They can also set budget and savings goals
        and update them at any time.
